name: amazon_price
description: You will be asked to estimate the Amazon price in USD for 20 products, given their image and specifications.

name: artists_name
description: You will be asked to listen to 20 short, 15-second audio clips of a song, and select the artist/band who interpreted each song.

name: ball_trick
description: You will be asked to watch 20 short videos of a magic trick, and identify the location of the ball at for each.

name: book_releaseyear
description: You will be asked to estimate the year of publication of 20 books, given the book’s name and author.

name: box_office_collection
description: You will be asked to estimate the international box office collection in millions of USD from the 20 Hollywood movies.

name: brands_popularity
description: Given two different brand for a product, you will be asked to select the brand that is most popular in a given market.

name: business_idea
description: You will be asked to indicate if a certain product will be funded or not by Kickstarter, given its image and a short description.

name: car_manufacture_year
description: You will shown 20 images of Ford cars, and asked to estimate the manufacture year of each car.

name: celeb_age
description: You will shown 20 images of celebrities, and asked to estimate the celebrity’s age.

name: celestial_bodies
description: You will shown 20 images of celestial bodies (stars, galaxies,planets, moons and asteroids) and asked to indicate their name.

name: classical_composition
description: You will be asked to listen to 20 audio clips of classical compositions, and asked to identify the composer.

name: classification_trees
description: You will shown 20 images of trees, and asked to select the correct species.

name: constellation_name
description: You will shown 20 images of constellations and asked to identify them by name.

name: construction_years
description: You will shown 20 images of famous buildings from around the world and asked to estimate how many years it took to build each.

name: container_size
description: You will shown 20 images of containers and asked to estimate its capacity.

name: country_currency
description: You will shown 20 images of monetary bills and asked to select the country where the currency is from.

name: country_flag
description: You will shown 20 images of flags, and asked to identify the country of origin.

name: country_landmass
description: You will given a list of 20 countries, and asked to estimate their landmass.

name: country_population
description: You will given a list of 20 countries, and asked to estimate their population.

name: country_shape
description: You will shown 20 images of country outlines, and asked to identify the country.

name: distance_map
description: You will be given a set of 20 city pairs, and asked to estimate the distance between two cities.

name: dog_breeds
description: You will be shown 20 images of dogs, and asked to identify the breed.

name: food_calories
description: You will be shown 20 images of food items, and asked to estimate the amount of calories present in each.

name: historical_events_II
description: You will be shown a list of five historical events. Select the option representing the correct chronological order of the historical events.

name: historical_monuments
description: You will be shown 20 images of architectural landmarks, and asked to select the country where the landmark is located.

name: human_emotions
description: You will be shown 20 images of individuals expressing an emotion, and asked to select the correct emotion.

name: imdb_rating
description: You will be shown 20 images of movie posters, and asked to estimate their IMDb rating from 0 to 10.

name: international_holidays
description: You will be given a list of 20 international holidays, and asked to input when they occurred in 2015.

name: language_script
description: You will be shown 20 sample texts, and asked to identify the language.

name: magazine_guesser
description: You will be given 20 headlines, and asked to select the magazine that published the article.

name: monuments_height
description: You will be shown 20 images of architectural landmarks along with their name and location, and asked to estimate their height.

name: movie_year
description: You will be asked to estimate the release year for a list of Hollywood films.

name: news_real
description: You will be given 20 headlines, and asked to identify whether each were real or fake.

name: object_weight
description: You will be shown 20 images of an everyday object, and asked to estimate its weight.

name: penalty_direction
description: You will be shown 20 videos of a soccer player about to take a penalty shot and asked to predict the direction which the ball will go. You will also be provided with the outcome of his last two attempted penalty shots.

name: retweets
description: You will be given 20 tweets from Katy Perry (an American singer and songwriter), and asked to predict the number of retweets each will accumulate.

name: sat_verbal
description: You will be given 20 words, and asked to identify the correct synonym corresponding to each word.

name: song_movie
description: You will be provided with 20 short audio files with theme songs from various movies, and asked to select the movie it was presented in.

name: tree_age
description: You will be shown 20 images of trees, and asked to estimate their age in years.

name: word_origin
description: You will be shown 20 words and asked to predict their origin.
